OL,4,Cdonation amid racism row
OL,6,FRishi Sunak is facing calls to hand
OL,7,Fback #10 million given to the
OL,8,FConservative Party after he condemned
OL,9,Fas "racist and wrong" comments
OL,10,Freportedly made by the major Tory
OL,11,Fbacker who donated the money.
OL,13,FFrank Hester is alleged to have said
OL,14,FDiane Abbott, Britain's longest-
OL,15,Fserving black MP, made him "want to
OL,16,Fhate all black women" and that she
OL,17,F"should be shot".
