OL,6,FThe Prime Minister had come under
OL,7,Fpressure over the remarks as Cabinet
OL,8,Fminister Kemi Badenoch broke ranks to
OL,9,Fsay they were racist while Downing
OL,10,FStreet continued to refuse to describe
OL,11,Fthem as such.
OL,13,FIn a new statement issued on Tuesday
OL,14,Fevening, the Prime Minister's
OL,15,Fspokesman said: "The comments
OL,16,Fallegedly made by Frank Hester were
OL,17,Fracist and wrong. He has now rightly
OL,18,Fapologised for the offence caused and
OL,19,Fwhere remorse is shown it should be
OL,20,Faccepted.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
