OL,6,F"The Prime Minister is clear there is
OL,7,Fno place for racism in public life
OL,8,Fand, as the first British-Asian Prime
OL,9,FMinister leading one of the most
OL,10,Fethnically diverse Cabinets in our
OL,11,Fhistory, the UK is living proof of
OL,12,Fthat fact."
OL,14,FMr Sunak faces a grilling by Labour
OL,15,Fleader Sir Keir Starmer during Prime
OL,16,FMinister's Questions later on
OL,17,FWednesday after the fallout
OL,18,Fintensified on Tuesday night following
OL,19,Fa Guardian report of further comments
OL,20,Fallegedly made by Mr Hester.
