OL,6,FAccording to the paper, Mr Hester, the
OL,7,Fchief executive of healthcare software
OL,8,Ffirm The Phoenix Partnership (TPP),
OL,9,Fasked if there was "no room for the
OL,10,FIndians" and suggested staff climb on
OL,11,Fa train roof during a crowded meeting.
OL,13,FHe has admitted making "rude" comments
OL,14,Fabout Ms Abbott, but claimed they had
OL,15,F"nothing to do with her gender nor
OL,16,Fcolour of skin".
OL,18,FThe PM's political opponents are
OL,19,Fdemanding that the #10 million donated
OL,20,Fby Mr Hester to the Conservative Party
OL,21,Fover the past year is returned.
