OL,6,FLabour Party chairwoman Anneliese
OL,7,FDodds said the Conservatives "must
OL,8,Fapologise unequivocally to Diane
OL,9,FAbbott, pay back these donations and
OL,10,Froot out the extreme views and
OL,11,Fprejudice which appears to be
OL,12,Ftolerated within the party."
OL,14,FMinisters sent out on Tuesday's
OL,15,Fmorning media round had defended Mr
OL,16,FHester while Number 10 said the
OL,17,Freported remarks about Ms Abbott were
OL,18,F"unacceptable", but would not describe
OL,19,Fthem as racist.
