OL,6,FBut, in a sign of divisions within the
OL,7,FTory Party over the issue, Business
OL,8,FSecretary Ms Badenoch became the first
OL,9,Fmember of Cabinet to call out Mr
OL,10,FHester's alleged words as racist on
OL,11,FTuesday afternoon.
OL,13,FMs Abbott herself said the reported
OL,14,Fcomments were "frightening" and
OL,15,F"alarming" given that two MPs ` Jo Cox
OL,16,Fand Sir David Amess ` had been
OL,17,Fmurdered in recent years.
