OL,6,FPolice are understood to have been
OL,7,Fcontacted about the remarks, with
OL,8,FScotland Yard saying officers from its
OL,9,FParliamentary Liaison and
OL,10,FInvestigation Team were in touch with
OL,11,Fan MP about a report in The Guardian,
OL,12,Fwhich broke the story.
OL,14,FLabour and the Liberal Democrats
OL,15,Fbranded Mr Hester's alleged remarks as
OL,16,F"clearly racist and abhorrent" and
OL,17,Fhave both urged the Tories to return
OL,18,Fthe money he donated to the party.
