OL,6,FThe Conservative Party has been
OL,7,Fapproached for comment on whether the
OL,8,Ffunds will be handed back.
OL,10,FIn a statement released via his firm,
OL,11,FMr Hester said he had rung Ms Abbott
OL,12,Fon Monday to "apologise directly for
OL,13,Fthe hurt he has caused her".
OL,15,F"He wishes to make it clear that he
OL,16,Fregards racism as a poison which has
OL,17,Fno place in public life," the
OL,18,Fstatement said.
