OL,6,FIn a statement posted on X on Tuesday
OL,7,Fafternoon, Mr Hester said: "The UK
OL,8,Fbenefits immensely from the rich
OL,9,Fdiversity of people ` like my parents
OL,10,F` who had roots in another land,
OL,11,Freligion and culture.
OL,13,F"We should celebrate those differences
OL,14,Fwhich have made us the world's most
OL,15,Fsuccessful multi-ethnic, multi-faith
OL,16,Fdemocracy.
OL,18,F"And we should have the confidence to
OL,19,Fdiscuss our differences openly and
OL,20,Feven playfully without seeking to
OL,21,Fcause offence."
